key "tong2004kinematic"

\end_inset

 and non-unitary evolution
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "carollo2003geometric"

\end_inset

.
 Especially in quantum information processing(QIP) domain, Berry Phase is
 deemed as a promising way to realize precise quantum control due to it's
 nature of immune to specific environmental noise.
 A numbers of experimental platforms have been put in Berry Phase such as
 NMR
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "jones2000geometric"

\end_inset

, superconducting circuit
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
