\end_inset

, and ultracold atoms
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "filipp2009experimental,richardson1988demonstration"

\end_inset

 in recent few years.
 Ion trap-based architectures are a promising solid-state platform for quantum
 information processing due to its high fidelity and long trapped time.
 Theoretical proposals
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
